Description: Nodetool Core - AI Workflow Engine library
 Nodetool Core is the core library for Nodetool, providing the necessary
 functionality for building and running AI workflows.
 .
 Key features include:
  - Node-Based DSL for declaring graphs in pure Python or JSON
  - First-class agent support with planner, browser, and tool-calling
  - Multi-provider AI integration (OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, Ollama)
  - WebSocket support for real-time updates
  - Async database operations with SQLite and PostgreSQL support
  - ChromaDB integration for vector storage
 .
 This package requires additional Python dependencies to be installed via pip.
 After installation, run: pip3 install --user nodetool-core
 to install the complete dependency tree.
